    <section class="app-c-banner app-c-banner--grid" aria-label="Notice">
      <h2 class="app-c-banner__title">Summary</h2>
  <p class="app-c-banner__desc">
          GLD is consulting on proposed changes to the Regional Panel Counsel

  </p>

    <p class="app-c-banner__desc">        This consultation ran from<br></br><span class="consultation-date"><time datetime="2017-03-23T09:00:00.000+00:00">9am on 23 March 2017</time> to
        <time datetime="2017-05-10T23:45:00.000+01:00">11:45pm on 10 May 2017</time></span>
</p>
</section>




    <div class="consultation-description">
      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Consultation description</h2>

      
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>Views are sought on proposals to alter both the structure of the Attorney General’s Regional Panel of civil counsel, and on and arrangements for recruiting to the Panel. GLD is also seeking views on what professional connection, if any, applicants should have with the Panel to which they apply.</p>
</div>
</div>


